caption.body: NOW PLAYING: A streetlamp, traffic signal, and stoplight perform a choreography at a lonely intersection of rural byways in San Pasqual High School student Howard Kung’s award-winning film for Walt Disney Family Museum’s 2019 Teen Animation International Festival.  See "The Lonely Stoplight" by Howard Kung, now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/307xG28
